name: TWISTERS I. SPECIAL EDITION OF NINE.
description:
Special TWISTERS item was created as a sign of the finishing of the first monochrome series.
Minted in edition of 10 copies. 

Series I contains of:
- TWISTER I-1 INTERPOLATION
- TWISTER I-2 BIPOLAR
- TWISTER I-3 WHITE NOISE
- TWISTER I-4 BLACK
- TWISTER I-5 GLITCH
- TWISTER I-6 LETTERS
- TWISTER I-7 BETRAYAL
- TWISTER I-8 SIMULACRUM

MP4, 2000x2000px


Original artwork by Olga Feldman.
